* Carnage snarled as she and Teltoli followed Cyber Claw, how dare 
this..this clone even try and imitate her dead friend!!! She was nothing 
like him, nothing! Sure her voice and looks almost matched but there was no 
way in the Pit that she could ever fool the Maximals into believing that she 
was Dinobot!
Carnage came up beside Cyber Claw...*

" You think to highly of yourself, you could never imitate Dinobot. That I 
know as a fact!"
